p__inner-container\">\n<h3><strong>Where to stay in Marseille<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The best place to stay in Marseille is anywhere near the old port (Vieux Port). It&#x2019;s right in the center of the old town and the best place to stay to see the sights and be at the heart of the action of the city.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/marseille-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to find view the hotels in the city.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/marseille-bw-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/19103701\/287121287-30x20.jpeg\" alt=\"BW Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/19103701\/287121287-450x300.jpeg\">\n                    <div class=\"product__content\">\n                        <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                        <div class=\"product__content-title\">BW Hotel<\/div>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        \n\n\n\n            <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/marseille-du-mondo-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                    <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/19103654\/284665907-30x30.jpeg\" alt=\"Convento Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"ht