           <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>Marseille also has its own airport which has flights leaving to many other international destinations. This makes it a very easy place to fly into on your French Riviera trip! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-marseille\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Find flights options here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera south france marseille\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera south france marseille\" class=\"wp-image-63478 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100216\/marseille-france-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.sa