\" rel=\"noopener\">Read more about Cassis in the Marseille travel guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3><strong>Where to Stay in Cassis<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cassis is small but there are plenty of great places to stay. If you&#x2019;re looking for a little more luxury, there are some incredible hotels that sit high above the town on the surrounding cliffs, with views of the sea. There are also local guest houses too, which are the perfect place to stay to be in the heart of Cassis. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/cassis-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here to view all available hotels.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/les-roches-blanches-cassis\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Les Roches Blanches\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/20093942\/Ho%CC%82tel-Les-Roches-Blanches-Cassis-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Les Roches Blanches<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/the-originals-boutique\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"The Originals Boutique\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/20093954\/The-Originals-Boutique-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">The Originals Boutique<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3><strong>Getting to Cassis<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cassis is only 30 minutes drive from Marseille, so use Marseille as your main hub for travel. From Marseille, you can travel to Cassis by train in 18 minutes, for as little as 5 EUR.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100154\/cassis-france-3.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera south france cassis\"><\/noscript><img width=\"265\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera south france cassis\" class=\"wp-image-63474 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1505px) 100vw, 1505px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100154\/cassis-france-3.jpg 1505w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100154\/cassis-france-3-470x600.jpg 470w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100154\/cassis-france-3-635x810.jpg 635w, https:\/\