 destination. Now, the colorful town is home to chic cafes, beautiful houses, and a harbor full of elegant yachts. One of the best things to do is come and people watch, and sit in one of the harbor-side restaurants, with a cocktail in hand.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-536x810.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france st tropez\"><\/noscript><img width=\"224\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france st tropez\" class=\"wp-image-63546 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 536px) 100vw, 536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-536x810.jpg 536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-397x600.jpg 397w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-224x338.jpg 224w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-108x163.jpg 108w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-119x180.jpg 119w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-508x768.jpg 508w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-677x1024.jpg 677w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-714x1080.jpg 714w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104626\/st-tropez-france-2-953x1440.jpg 953w, https:\/\/static.sa