ck-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Saint-Tropez has a citadel that sits high up on the hill above the town. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to go and catch some magical views, especially at sunset or sunrise.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france st tropez\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france st tropez\" class=\"wp-image-63543 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104616\/st-tropez-france-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/