ntainer\">\n<h2 id=\"h-day-6-cannes-or-antibes\">Day 6: Cannes (or Antibes)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Known for the Cannes Film festival, the city is often in the spotlight as a place for celebrities, bringing it a certain exclusivity. However, it&#x2019;s still a charming port town and there are ways to enjoy it without breaking the bank! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-541x810.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france cannes\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france cannes\" class=\"wp-image-63539 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 541px) 100vw, 541px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-541x810.jpg 541w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-401x600.jpg 401w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-513x768.jpg 513w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-684x1024.jpg 684w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-france-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104558\/cannes-f