 Antibes! <\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Getting to Cannes<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Reach Cannes from Saint-Tropez by car in 2 hours or by train from Nice in under half an hour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france cannes\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"286\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france cannes\" class=\"wp-image-63537 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-1080x686.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-450x286.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-30x19.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-163x103.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-284x180.jpg 284w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-768x488.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-1024x650.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-1440x914.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/01104548\/cannes-france-1-600x381.jpg 600w\" tem