\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In the evening, take a picnic of food you&#x2019;ve bought from the market and head to the top of Castle Hill. Here you&#x2019;ll discover panoramic views out across <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/nice-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Nice<\/a> and the surrounding coastline; it&#x2019;s the perfect place to sit as the sun goes down.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Nice is oozing with history. One of the most unusual historical buildings is the Russian Orthodox Cathedral, known as one of the most impressive of its type outside of Russia itself.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100545\/nice-france-4-1-578x810.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france nice\"><\/noscript><img width=\"241\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france nice\" class=\"wp-image-63510 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100545\/nice-france-4-1-578x810.jpg 578w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100545\/nice-france-4-1-428x600.jpg 428w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-con