Cannes to Nice run regularly and take about 35 minutes. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/trains\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your train connection here.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/nice-things-to-do\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete Nice, France travel guide<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/63196&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02144755\/french-riviera-3.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02144755\/french-riviera-3-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02144755\/french-riviera-3-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"South of France: The Ultimate 12-Day Travel Itinerary\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-day-9-villefranche-sur-mer\">Day 9: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/villefranche-sur-mer\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Villefranche-sur-Mer<\/a><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Villefranche-sur-Mer is the hidden gem of the French Riviera. It&#x2019;s much quieter than some of the more popular neighboring cities and towns on the coastline and this adds to its charm. Every old building has been beautifully preserved and it&#x2019;s so picturesque that it&#x2019;s been the setting for many famous films.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100656\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-4.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\" class=\"wp-image-63524 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100656\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-4.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100656\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-4-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100656\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-4-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100656\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/st