ure: a 13th-century passageway that goes under the old town.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Finish your day at the Plage des Marinieres. This is a beautiful bay, with perfect water for swimming, which looks across to the colorful old town.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\" class=\"wp-image-63526 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100706\/Villefranche-sur-Mer-france-5-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/stati