ss=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotel: 75 &#x2013; 300 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Guesthouse: 20 &#x2013; 70 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 15 &#x2013; 50 USD\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 20 USD per day\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to Travel Around the French Riviera<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Traveling around the French Riviera is super easy by car but also via public transport. There are great rail links between all the towns and tickets are generally very cheap (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/trains\/\">Find train tickets<\/a>). There are public buses but roads can be busy at peak times on the coastal roads. Additionally, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">hiring a car<\/a> can give you the freedom to explore hidden corners of the French Riviera but make sure to factor in the costs of parking in the cities and towns.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>By car:<\/strong> To travel around the French Riviera we recommend <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/rent-car-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">renting a car in France<\/a> at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and all insurance is included (so no surprises when you pick up your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"besttime\">Best Time to Travel to the French Riviera<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The French Riviera is the warmest place in France, with over 300 days of sunshine a year! The summers are hot and dry, spring and fall are still warm, and the winters are mild. This means that any time is good to travel to the French Riviera. If you want fewer crowds and lower prices, we recommend traveling during the spring or fall.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"french riviera travel guide south france\" class=\"wp-image-63494 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/01100406\/menton-france-4-1-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp